    A - &gt; B -&gt; { X -&gt; Y -&gt; Z } -&gt; C

Where I can expose the `{ X -&gt; Y -&gt; Z }` pipeline to my application layer and not be concerned with mutations affecting the pipeline I control.

Is there any clean way to simulate this behavior?

